Attachments
precis:
Authority for the Minister of Indian Affairs and Northern Development to
sign (a) an UMBRELLA FINAL AGREEMENT which sets out the framework within
which Yukon First Nations may negotiate comprehensive land claim
agreements, and
(b) FINAL AGREEMENTS with each of the following Yukon native peoples,
namely:
.
  1. The Vuntut Gwitchin First Nation
  2. The First Nation of Nacho Nyak Dun
  3. The Champagne and Aishihik First Nations
  4. The Teslin Tlingit Council
.
